  Drop mobile herd as talked in gentoo-dev ML

  04 May 2012; Jeff Horelick <jdhore@gentoo.org> airsnort-0.2.7e.ebuild:
  dev-util/pkgconfig -> virtual/pkgconfig

  02 Apr 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> airsnort-0.2.7e.ebuild:
  Use net-libs/libpcap instead of virtual/libpcap wrt #358835.

  16 Oct 2009; Thilo Bangert <bangert@gentoo.org> airsnort-0.2.7e.ebuild:
  einfo -> elog

  12 Mar 2008; Christian Heim <phreak@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Removing Peter Johanson (latexer, #206688) from metadata.xml.

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  23 Oct 2006; Stefan Schweizer <genstef@gentoo.org>
  -airsnort-0.2.1a.ebuild, -airsnort-0.2.1b.ebuild, -airsnort-0.2.2.ebuild,
